		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Mobile optimization and responsive design]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.scrollstudios.com/en/projects/sites-optimizados-para-iphone/" />
		<id>http://www.scrollstudios.com/?p=413</id>
		<updated>2011-10-25T18:16:04Z</updated>
		<published>2011-10-23T16:42:46Z</published>
		<category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="blog-entries" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="clients" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="iphone optimization" />		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[Our clients Hook Management, Sebastian Liste and Cyan understood that everytime more users are surfing the internet from their smartphones and tablets. For this reason they asked us to optimized their sites for mobile devices, specially for Iphone...]]></summary>
		<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.scrollstudios.com/en/projects/sites-optimizados-para-iphone/"><![CDATA[<p>Our clients<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.hookmanagement.net/" target="_blank"> Hook Management</a>, <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.sebastianliste.com/" target="_blank"> Sebastian Liste</a> and <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.somoscyan.com" target="_blank">Cyan</a> understood that everytime more users are surfing the internet from their <strong>smartphones</strong> or <strong>tablets</strong>. For this reason they asked us to optimized their sites for mobile devices, specially for <strong>iPhone</strong> but also for <strong>Android</strong> and <strong>Blackberry</strong>.</p>
<p>To improve the user experience in this kind of devices: We reduced the content of their sites, avoided uncomfortable zooms, simplified the layout and we had on mind the tactile dimension of these devices.</p>
<p>This kind of optimization did not change their content publishing workflow, and did not imply a double site maintenance either because it&#8217;s only one website adapting to different devices.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-479" title="scroll-iphone2" src="http://www.scrollstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/scroll-iphone2.jpg" alt="" width="745" height="1505" /></p>
]]></content>
