		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Thomas Giddings &#8211; fashion photographer]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.scrollstudios.com/en/projects/thomas-giddings-photographer/" />
		<id>/scrollstudios/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php?lang=es</id>
		<updated>2010-07-19T09:39:43Z</updated>
		<published>2010-04-19T12:53:55Z</published>
		<category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="CMS" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="web development" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="Interface design" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="web design" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="Blog migration" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="projects-entries" /><category scheme="http://www.scrollstudios.com" term="wireframing" />		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[Thomas contacted us because he couldn't update his old website easily. We designed and developed a new portfolio website that highlights his great shots.]]></summary>
		<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.scrollstudios.com/en/projects/thomas-giddings-photographer/"><![CDATA[<p>Thomas Giddings is a fashion photographer. He has shot for various clients including British and Russian Vogue, i-D, Jalouse, Topman and Mulberry. He balances his commercial work with personal projects and has recently had his second solo photography show in London where he is currently based.</p>
<p>Thomas contacted us because he couldn&#8217;t update his old website easily. He also had a blog that was not integrated into his site. We designed and developed a new portfolio website, highlighting his work by utilising the entire width of the screen. We also implemented an easy and engaging navigation system and integrated his blog making it more personal and visually more interesting.</p>
<p>After finishing Thomas’s website we were contacted by other clients from the fashion industry, leading to a new website and an online shop coming soon…</p>
]]></content>
